        Neither describes a 25-bed critical access hospital, which is the gap a managed service is built for. See the
        full buyer view in <a href="/critical-access-hospital-scheduling">critical access hospital scheduling</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>How Does SimpleScheduleAI Deliver AI Nurse Scheduling as a Managed Service?</h2>
